Telkom has revealed its Big Deal for October 2018 – a 40GB+20GB LTE package. The deal is based on a SmartBroadband Wireless 10GB package, but includes additional data. Users will receive: Telkom said the Huawei B525 router provides download speeds of up to 300Mbps and upload speeds of up to 50Mbps. It also supports up to 64 devices, and an RJ11 port for a voice connection. The deal is valid until 31 October 2018 or while stocks last. Users are advised to check Telkom’s LTE coverage map before purchasing the deal to ensure they are in an LTE-covered area. The video below provides a short overview of the deal. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>